---
title: Quick Chorizo Flatbread Pizzas with Pickled Jalapeños and Onions
description: Jump on the train to flavour town with this speedy chorizo flatbread pizza. Your taste buds will go wild for the quick-pickled onions and jalapeños, salty feta and zesty lime mayo finish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pizzas-sur-pains-plats-au-chorizo-3c5a5b44.jpg
